---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro'
import { pageTitle } from '../lib/site'
---

<Base title={pageTitle('origins')}>
  <style>
    .eyebrow {
      font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--dim); display: flex; align-items: baseline; gap: 10px;
    }
    .eyebrow .num { font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; color: var(--accent); }
    .sec { padding: 56px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-soft); }
    .sec:last-of-type { border-bottom: 0; }
    .sec .wrap { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 160px 1fr; gap: 48px; }
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .sec { padding: 44px 0; } .sec .wrap { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 20px; }
    }
    .lede {
      font-family: var(--serif);
      font-size: 20px; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.5; color: var(--fg);
      max-width: 38ch; margin: 0;
    }
    .lede em { font-style: italic; color: var(--muted); }
    .prose { font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--muted); max-width: 60ch; }
    .prose p + p { margin-top: 14px; }
    .prose a { color: var(--fg); text-decoration: underline; text-decoration-color: var(--dim); text-underline-offset: 2px; }
    .prose a:hover { color: var(--accent); }
    .prose .name { color: var(--fg); font-weight: 500; }

    .credit-row {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 180px 1fr; gap: 20px;
      padding: 14px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.55;
    }
    .credit-row:last-child { border-bottom: 0; }
    .credit-row .who { color: var(--fg); }
    .credit-row .role { color: var(--muted); }
    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      .credit-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 4px; }
      .credit-row .role { color: var(--dim); }
    }

    .attribution {
      margin-top: 20px; padding: 16px 18px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      background: var(--surface);
      font-size: 11.5px; line-height: 1.65; color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 60ch;
    }
    .attribution .k { color: var(--dim); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.14em; font-size: 9px; margin-right: 8px; }
  </style>

  <section class="sec">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div><div class="eyebrow"><span class="num">00</span><span>Origins</span></div></div>
      <div>
        <p class="lede">
          Cathedral runs on an engine we did not build.
          <em>The story it tells is ours.</em>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="sec">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div><div class="eyebrow"><span class="num">01</span><span>The engine</span></div></div>
      <div>
        <div class="prose">
          <p>
            Cathedral's technical foundation is <a href="https://github.com/tplr-ai/basilica">Basilica</a>,
            a Bittensor-native compute verification subnet built by the
            <span class="name">Covenant AI</span> team between 2025 and 2026.
            Basilica is the part that inspects the metal: SSH-based hardware attestation,
            a validator that actually verifies GPUs, and a miner framework home
            operators can run. That engineering is what makes any of this possible.
          </p>
          <p>
            Upstream continues to ship. Cathedral is a fork of that codebase.
            Without it there is no cathedral; only an idea.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="sec">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div><div class="eyebrow"><span class="num">02</span><span>Engineering credits</span></div></div>
      <div>
        <div class="credit-row">
          <div class="who"><span class="name">Evan Pappas</span> · <span class="role">epappas</span></div>
          <div class="role">Lead engineer, Basilica</div>
        </div>
        <div class="credit-row">
          <div class="who"><span class="name">itzlambda</span></div>
          <div class="role">Lead engineer, Basilica</div>
        </div>
        <div class="credit-row">
          <div class="who"><span class="name">open-junius</span></div>
          <div class="role">Foundational verification work · Opentensor Foundation</div>
        </div>
        <div class="credit-row">
          <div class="who"><span class="name">Covenant AI</span></div>
          <div class="role">Original team</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="sec">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div><div class="eyebrow"><span class="num">03</span><span>What's ours</span></div></div>
      <div>
        <div class="prose">
          <p>
            Cathedral is not Basilica with a new name. The engine verifies hardware;
            Cathedral is what we build with it — home-ownable compute as a commons,
            the medieval-trades vocabulary, the audience of home operators and
            global-south mason cohorts, and the business model being worked out
            one stone at a time.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="sec">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div><div class="eyebrow"><span class="num">04</span><span>License</span></div></div>
      <div>
        <div class="attribution">
          <div><span class="k">License</span>MIT — inherited from Basilica. See
          <a href="https://github.com/cathedralai/cathedral/blob/main/LICENSE" style="color: var(--fg);">LICENSE</a>
          in the repository for the full text.</div>
          <div style="margin-top: 8px;"><span class="k">Upstream</span>
          <a href="https://github.com/tplr-ai/basilica" style="color: var(--fg);">github.com/tplr-ai/basilica</a></div>
          <div style="margin-top: 8px;"><span class="k">This fork</span>
          <a href="https://github.com/cathedralai/cathedral" style="color: var(--fg);">github.com/cathedralai/cathedral</a></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
